<br>
Every day i see less and less wizards because unless you solo your way up you cant get in a group.  How many times have we waited at zone in in velks/guk/seb shouting for a group to no avail.  We dont have any apeals unless they need us for a larger raid. And that is real issue at hand making wizards group friendly and or desirable.  <br>
<br>
Well that is my two cents<br>
<br>
Nords<br>
Lv 58 Wizard <br>
