<br>
Anyways...<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Kinda cracks me up, that they are improving an aspect of our class and people complain. In the same note, they said that this was one of the changes (plural) in the works.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
Note: Ancient spells in games are.... level 60! Yay! That eliminates a vast amount of wizards from being balanced. Also note they said they are going to be -RARE-. Yup. Er wait... melee weapons are rare too - right? right? How many times have you killed a dragon in ToV and seen it itemless or not drop a melee item? That level 51 warrior who just stood around and looked pretty got ToV item! Yay! ~100 dragons later, an ancient spell! JOY! Time to random, whoop wait, favoritism accusations blah blah blah.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Out of curiosity, how many of you wizards that complain, have played a melee class in Luclin in..say...the Temple of Ssra. If you have, you'll see that the AC on these mobs is insanely high, thus each round of melee for the &quot;overpowered&quot; tanks hits for substantially less than ...say....a froglok from Sebilis. If you're smart, and you cast the correct line of spells on these same mobs, your &quot;unbalanced&quot; ass will deliver precisely the same amount of damage as it would on same froglok in seb.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
Yes, and damage is a prime source of taunt. This is one of the problems with EQ. If not enough taunt is being generated, then the casters and clerics are in trouble, possibly turning your pull into an aggro kite. If I'm smart, I'll cast the correct line of spells. Yup... I'm gonna go wax that stupid snake with Sunstrike erm... wait, nm. I don't have Sunstrike, /cry because its rarer than the rarest piece of melee crap. Guess I gotta use Draught of Fire.<br>
<br>
Personally, in my opinion, balance can not be addressed by dropping new issues on old ones. The problems with balance, in my opinion, revolve around:<br>
<br>
*The required need of damage to taunt and maintain aggro<br>
*The drop rate of spells<br>
*The &quot;commonity&quot; of decent, high end melee items<br>
*The no-drop of decent melee items<br>
*The failure of spells to continue to scale upwards after next spell level<br>
<br>
And under all of this:<br>
<br>
*The set-in-stone mentallity of people of what a raid or group 'requires'<br>
<br>
In my opinion, giving me more level 60 spells isn't going to fix me, it is just going to give me a bigger option of spells to throw against my target.  And quanity does not equal quality.<br>
<br>
-Ikeya <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showMessageRange?topicID=672.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showMessageRange?topicID=672.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showMessageRange?topicID=672.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showMessageRange?topicID=672.topic&start=81&stop=100>5</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showMessageRange?topicID=672.topic&start=101&stop=120>6</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showMessageRange?topicID=672.topic&start=121&stop=140>7</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showMessageRange?topicID=672.topic&start=141&stop=160>8</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showMessageRange?topicID=672.topic&start=161&stop=180>9</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showMessageRange?topicID=672.topic&start=181&stop=200>10</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showMessageRange?topicID=672.topic&start=201&stop=203>11</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showPrevMessage?topicID=672.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showNextMessage?topicID=672.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.emailToFriend?topicID=672.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboar